        INPUT:

        - ``other`` -- A matroid.

        OUTPUT:

        A dictionary, or ``None``

        EXAMPLES::

            sage: M1 = matroids.Wheel(3)
            sage: M2 = matroids.CompleteGraphic(4)
            sage: morphism=M1.isomorphism(M2)
            sage: M1.is_isomorphism(M2, morphism)
